ality test using an inequality, and we reveal non-trivial genuine\nhigh-order correlation in the GBS samples, which are evidence of robustness\nagainst possible classical simulation schemes. The photonic quantum computer,\nJiuzhang 2.0, yields a Hilbert space dimension up to $10^{43}$, and a sampling\nrate $10^{24}$ faster than using brute-force simulation on supercomputers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jun 2021 16:11:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Jul 2021 16:15:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-03"}
