antum Lifshitz Model\" -- that illustrates the critical\ndrag mechanism as well as the other considerations of the paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jun 2021 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 4 Sep 2021 21:17:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 19:53:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
