ns at $\\nu_{\\rm max} \\lesssim\n100\\,\\mu\\textrm{Hz}$ but it cannot account for the population of red giants\nthat exhibit dipole modes with unusually small amplitudes at high $\\nu_{\\rm\nmax}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Jun 2021 18:41:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
