requencies, amplitudes and propagation angles.\nOur work proposes an explanation for the observations of oblique and parallel\nwhistler waves in the solar wind. We conclude that solar wind expansion has to\nbe factored in when trying to explain kinetic processes at different\nheliocentric distances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 10:42:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Jul 2021 14:25:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-29"}
