ty evolution of electrode\nmaterials during cycling of importance for battery design, and also point to\npathways for forming materials with thermally switchable properties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 13:10:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Sep 2021 01:48:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-10"}
