\nbecause the amount of mass ejected is negligible. These predictions will be\neasily tested with the new generation of detectors if Black Holes with an\nadimensional spin parameter $\\chi_\\mathrm{BH}\\gtrsim 0.2$ or a mass $\\mathrm\nM_\\mathrm{BH} \\lesssim 4 \\mathrm M_\\odot$ can be present in the merger.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 15:50:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 May 2022 16:01:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-30"}
