6 VRS was assessed in a listening test conducted with a\nspherical loudspeaker array within an anechoic room. For the resulting low\nnumbers of VRS suited for spatial rendering, optimal physically-based parameter\nchoices for the FDN are discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 30 Jun 2021 08:33:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-30"}
